{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">1-3 PLAYER ONLINE CO-OP HOLY BRETHREN</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/PriestGIF.gif?t=1727149723\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>HOLY PURGE is a co-op exorcist horror survival game for up to 3 players.</strong><br>Play as Holy Priests and work together to exorcise evil.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BIBLE CAMP MAP</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/store_page_demonflyburn.jpg?t=1727149723\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Investigate a bible camp for missing children and repel flying demons who possess them.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VILLAGE MAP</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/Village_Gif_8mb.gif?t=1727149723\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Complete the ritual and cleanse a plague befalling a medieval village.</strong><br>Collect ritual items to reverse a witch spell and defend yourselves using holy crosses, silver, and fire torches against werewolves and demons.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXORCIST MAP</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/Exorcist_gif_8mb.gif?t=1727149723\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Perform an exorcism on a woman possessed by a demon.</strong><br>Find demonic spirits lurking within a house. Use items to banish these spirits and cleanse the house to weaken the grip on a possessed woman.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/3.gif?t=1727149723\" /><br>Exorcise a possessed daughter and bring her back to life.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/Reaper.gif?t=1727149723\" /><br>Work together with your fellow brethren and overcome an ancient evil spirit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REPLAY-ABILITY</h2>    <br>Doors, ritual Items and collectibles are randomized.<br>Explore each map background lore by reading all notes and cassette messages.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DIFFICULTY</h2>Replay maps with increased difficulty for an increasingly terrifying experience<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SINGLE PLAYER</h2>For hardcore players only. Do it all by yourself. For those who possess the strongest of faith, and therefore the ability to take on the evil alone.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WARNING</h2>This game contains flashing lights that may make it unsuitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy or other photosensitive conditions. Player discretion is advised.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"HOLY MISSION","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1844060/5cdb120810c6cd8a5ff44c60bb3b349ca6442a4a.jpg"},{"name":"WITCH RITUAL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1844060/fd9e320cafd718b811826e4b1d748019ff911216.jpg"},{"name":"SOUL POSSESSED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1844060/7a6886d11937374c2de6e3a80195859ac6e792d8.jpg"},{"name":"EVIL PREVAILS","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1844060/76bc955f8f7a801cf7edf33cecaf409023d24c52.jpg"},{"name":"HOLY RITUAL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1844060/b687f9bbc47ae0e2701128a2bbadd1021084eac2.jpg"},{"name":"HOLY HEALERS","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1844060/3c0b26e933becc51d2191b3049f666533c811ff4.jpg"},{"name":"GOD REIGNS SUPREME","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1844060/e81b83d2d8e2cdaaba85e8ce1077b7cbf47bb9b7.jpg"},{"name":"OLD TRADITIONS","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1844060/5a4018d4f1e3b6c84e12